RACE.FOOTNOTES: SWEET ALEX went to an early pressured lead to set all the pace then inched away at the quarter pole to be an easy winner. BABY LIAISON was off the pace down the backstretch then was asked at the five sixteenth pole and made a three wide bid but was no match for the winner.
